channel.title: Nulls connecting to server
channel.description:
My server is lagging heavily. About every 3-5 seconds a "null" connects to my server. My server disconnects it, however 3 seconds later a new one comes in.
Heres a picture: [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/2le1p2u.jpg[/img]
It just continues and continues. How do I get it to stop lagging my server.
Thanks, Rich Dude99

item.title: Nulls connecting to server

item.description:
@airborne wrote:

i dont really know about this, but on my server, the null is a person trying to connect from a client uncompatable with the server. Tell people to use the client used, and not others. Please tell me if this helped.
